		<h2 class='flexible-html-title flexible-title'>		A tailor-made offer		</h2>
				
		<div class="flexible-html-content post-content"><p style="text-align: left;"><div class='col-row auto-height-wrapper'><div class='col-half'></p>
<p>All our offers are unique and aim to best respond to your particular needs. You choose:</p>
<p><strong>• Your chauffeur</strong>: we will present you with several candidates who meet your selected criteria, in order to guarantee the success of the placement</p>
<p><strong>• Your vehicle</strong>: brand, color, options – you decide</p>
<p><strong>• Your plan</strong>: from 5 hours of service per day to 12 hours, we will offer you a plan based on your needs</p>
<p><strong>• Your schedule</strong>: the chauffeur will adapt to your schedule in order to guarantee an optimal use of your plan</p>
<p><strong>• Your management service</strong>: billing, reports, chauffeur communication, etc. We will make a selection of tools available to you for the efficient management of your contract</p>
